{"tid":2175893,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"柳俊江: 警方已猶如活在自己的王國 超越指鹿為馬地抹黑史實 猶如納粹德軍般的極權","createTime":"2020-08-26T17:56:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-27T13:37:57.000Z","uid":240362,"like":41,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"266794328ac3ec90a8571c8b3444f67d75fe91d5","tid":2175893,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T17:56:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200827/XJCDLTLWCNEX5I6E4GYSY7CEBU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200827%2FXJCDLTLWCNEX5I6E4GYSY7CEBU%2F&d=hjP0Q4X6c9sJGZoCRXhatq0EM2ZTCgB2Df5M2YAuo3Y%3D&h=8b173198\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200827%2FXJCDLTLWCNEX5I6E4GYSY7CEBU%2F&h=2ceb8b81\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200827/XJCDLTLWCNEX5I6E4GYSY7CEBU/</a><br />\n.<br />\n作為一個本地記者，有幾個在職業生涯中要直視活生生的新聞打壓？資深傳媒人柳俊江形容，今日警方已猶如活在自己的王國內，擁有一己的政治操作，不需要再為香港政府或是任何派別去服務，甚至連「法律程序已經唔係一套值得（警方）尊重嘅嘢」，只不斷做壯大聲威的「打飛機」舉止，「超越指鹿為馬」地抹黑史實。他形容面對猶如納粹德軍般的極權，無法埋身肉搏，認為市民必須加強對真相的尋求，記住今天的所有事。"},{"pid":"2ba190e5a2c14e7f1119bf1991c5bed988150cf3","tid":2175893,"uid":342786,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T18:00:45.000Z","msg":"指鹿為馬唔係為左欺騙<br />\n而係要搵出反對既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n趙高欲為亂，恐群臣不聽，乃先設驗，持鹿獻於二世，曰: 「馬也。 」，二世笑曰: 「丞相誤邪? 謂鹿為馬。 」，問左右，左右或默，或言馬以順趙高。"},{"pid":"bd3fd2ffcbc9b2490bf620d0b8ad5b9ce7256433","tid":2175893,"uid":324629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ba190e5a2c14e7f1119bf1991c5bed988150cf3","tid":2175893,"uid":342786,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T18:00:45.000Z","msg":"指鹿為馬唔係為左欺騙<br />\n而係要搵出反對既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n趙高欲為亂，恐群臣不聽，乃先設驗，持鹿獻於二世，曰: 「馬也。 」，二世笑曰: 「丞相誤邪? 謂鹿為馬。 」，問左右，左右或默，或言馬以順趙高。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T18:05:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4825612482ef0633164d59c560afaac42cd6140a","tid":2175893,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T18:12:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9995eefdb51500f102266aec149a9259c35de76","tid":2175893,"uid":354682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T01:27:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46f6caf0ade0e063661c28a515d2384a9f3fdd13","tid":2175893,"uid":34899,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T13:37:57.000Z","msg":"係日匪皇軍"}]}